sequenceDiagram
    participant DSP as DSP API Server
    participant K8s as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant WFC as workflow-controller<br/>9090/TCP Metrics<br/>6060/TCP Health
    participant Pod as Workflow Step Pod
    participant Exec as argoexec Sidecar
    participant User as User Container
    participant S3 as Artifact Repository<br/>(S3/MinIO/GCS)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over DSP,S3: Flow 1: Workflow Execution

    DSP->>K8s: 1. Create Workflow CR<br/>HTTPS/443 | SA Token
    K8s-->>WFC: 2. Watch notification (Workflow created)<br/>HTTPS | SA Token
    WFC->>K8s: 3. Create step Pod<br/>HTTPS/443 | SA Token

    Note over Pod,S3: Pod starts with argoexec + user container

    activate Pod
    activate Exec

    Exec->>S3: 4. Download input artifacts<br/>HTTPS/443 | IAM/AccessKey
    S3-->>Exec: Artifact data

    activate User
    Note over User: 5. Execute ML pipeline step
    User->>User: Write outputs to<br/>/var/run/argo/outputs/
    deactivate User

    Exec->>Exec: Compress output artifacts (tar.gz)
    Exec->>S3: 5. Upload output artifacts<br/>HTTPS/443 | IAM/AccessKey
    Exec->>K8s: 6. Create WorkflowTaskResult CR<br/>HTTPS/443 | SA Token

    deactivate Exec
    deactivate Pod

    K8s-->>WFC: 7. Watch notification (TaskResult)<br/>HTTPS | SA Token
    WFC->>K8s: Update Workflow status<br/>HTTPS/443 | SA Token

    Note over DSP,S3: Flow 2: Artifact Management Detail

    rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
        Note over Exec,S3: Init Container Phase
        Exec->>S3: Download input artifacts<br/>HTTPS/443 | IAM/AccessKey
        S3-->>Exec: Artifact files

        Note over User: Main Container Phase
        User->>User: Process data<br/>Write to /var/run/argo/outputs/

        Note over Exec,S3: Wait/Sidecar Phase
        Exec->>Exec: Read /var/run/argo/outputs/<br/>Compress to tar.gz
        Exec->>S3: Upload output artifacts<br/>HTTPS/443 | IAM/AccessKey
    end
